reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Most cost effective option; great quality
reviews.reviewText: I am a media creator (especially video) so I need to store large amounts of data for my clients as well as myself. I repurpose old Hard Drives to save money and archive all footage. This box allows me to safely store them and forget about it. I do not use the keys/lock mechanism as there is no sensitive material but I tried it out and they seem to be functioning properly. Other Hard Drive boxes cost much more but this one seems to be well manufactured.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for all you data hoarders out there
reviews.reviewText: I am shockingly pleased with how well made this hard drive case is, I have been looking for storage for three and a half and two and a half inch hard drives for a good while now and most of the listings that I have found previously were well over $60 even on AliExpress, it seems like it has good padding definitely not going to be adequate if you're going to put it on an airplane or really move it more than to your car and home, I do not think that it would do much against a decently hard impact but I definitely think that it is a great way to store hard drives if you have an access that are just stacked on top of each other

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Does what I need it to do
reviews.reviewText: Needed an inexpensive storage container for some old NAS HDD's I'm retiring - they fit snugly in the box, closes properly, locks properly (little finicky but works). Quality seems mediocre, mine also had a bunch of dried on glue on the outside that's been a pain to try and get off. Overall I'm satisfied with what I received.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very nice protection for my old HD's drives
reviews.reviewText: I'm extremely pleased with the quality of the storage container.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 27, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good Protection Suitcase for HDs
reviews.reviewText: This suitcase hold and protects internal laptop/PC hard disks. Very good product, good for the money.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 21, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It does the trick
reviews.reviewText: This is a handy storage case for my 3.5 drives. The foam slots for the drives seem fine as far as anti-static concerns go. I was a little concerned that the lid closed a little too tightly on the drives, but this concern is not valid. The case secures the drives so that they won't flop around but does not crush the drives. I like it enough so that I may buy another.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great item, does its job
reviews.reviewText: Great item, smaller than I expected but works great for bare hard drive storage. Drives cannot be put in slot with anti-static bags, but otherwise holds 8 3.5s, 6 2.5s and a slot for USB/m.2 Sata/NVMe Drives if you wish
